snippet.title: The Garden Path Release Date Trailer
snippet.description: EXCLUSIVE: The Garden Path sprouts on July 30th! Featured in Wholesome Direct, this slice-of-life sim about gardening and making new friends will be released on Steam (PC/Mac), @itchio, and #NintendoSwitch 🌱 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1638500/The_Garden_Path #indiegames #nintendoswitch #cozygames
